altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 32
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 32
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v32 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Pokémon XD: Gale of Darkness, Super Mario Strikers, and Mario Party 7. The disc also features videos for the following: Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance, Game Boy Micro, Need for Speed: Most Wanted, Tony Hawk's American Wasteland, Super Mario Strikers, X-Men Legends II: Rise of Apocalypse, Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire, Shadow the Hedgehog, Dance Dance Revolution: Mario Mix, The Sims 2, Mario Party 7, NBA Live 06, SSX on Tour, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
